pageContext.description: Typology: Corp's Tongue sword. Tong has 3 rivet holes, centre on is incomplete, rivet found in bottom hole. Short fat ribs join shoulder rivet holes with bottom hole on tong.,Condition: incomplete. Broken into at least 3 parts in antiquity by bending into V shape, tip missing. Signs of edge-on-edge damage on blade.
